            . I am a <rs id="t18310908-400-viclabel2060" type="occupation">stage-coachman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-400-victim2856 t18310908-400-viclabel2060"></join>, and live at <placeName id="t18310908-400-crimeloc2061">Hammersmith</placeName>
